shortDescription: Snuggle into the airy softness of the Diamond Gauze Quilt.  Two layers of 100% cotton gauze create the casual crinkled texture. The reverse is a super soft brushed polyester.  This versatile new classic will layer beautifully with your existing bedding or look perfect on its own.  The kantha style quilting done in a classic diamond pattern gives it a hand-crafted look.  Available colors include Papyrus Beige, Green River, and Aged Blue.  Imported China.
